snippet.textDisplay: Wow. This girl has a rustic, folksy quality to her voice. I think most people have not heard this kind of music. If you live in the Sindhi or Saraiki belt there are lots of voices like this. The music seems slightly off though. The voices and music don't seem to jell. This was not too bad. Some people seem to have a very visceral negative reaction to this one.
